01:20:13,321 --> 01:20:15,323
Sayang, ayolah.
Ini hanya permainan.

917
01:20:21,496 --> 01:20:22,664
Bagus, Sayang.

918
01:20:43,351 --> 01:20:45,103
- Apa yang kau lakukan?
- Ayolah.

919
01:21:03,204 --> 01:21:04,706
Monyet kesayanganku.

920
01:21:19,220 --> 01:21:20,054
Berhenti!

