927
01:22:22,992 --> 01:22:24,827
Aku yakin ini punya kalian.

928
01:22:28,455 --> 01:22:30,749
- Terima kasih.
- Aku Laurent.

929
01:22:31,708 --> 01:22:33,043
Ini Victoria…

930
01:22:35,003 --> 01:22:36,213
dan James.

931
01:22:37,673 --> 01:22:39,716
Aku Carlisle. Ini keluargaku.

932
01:22:42,094 --> 01:22:42,970
Halo.

933
01:22:43,554 --> 01:22:47,015
Kegiatan berburu kalian
membuat kami terganggu.

934
01:22:47,099 --> 01:22:51,395
